\c 13
\s Ukwehlukana kukaAbrama loLothi
\p
\v 1 UAbrama wasesenyuka eGibithe, yena lomkakhe lakho konke ayelakho loLothi kanye laye, waya eningizimu.
\v 2 Njalo uAbrama wayenothile kakhulu\x + Zaga 10.22.\x*, ngezifuyo, ngesiliva, langegolide.
\v 3 Wasehamba kubuhambuma bakhe esuka eningizimu, waze wafika eBhetheli, endaweni lapho ithente lakhe elalikhona kuqala, phakathi kweBhetheli leAyi;
\v 4 endaweni yelathi ayelenzile khona kuqala\x + 12.7,8.\x*; uAbrama wasebiza ibizo leN\sc KOSI\sc* lapho.
\p
\v 5 LoLothi laye, owayehamba loAbrama, wayelezimvu lezinkomo lamathente.
\v 6 Njalo ilizwe lalingabathwali ukuthi bahlale ndawonye\x + 36.7.\x*, ngoba impahla yabo yayinengi, ukuthi babengeke bahlala ndawonye.
\v 7 Kwasekusiba khona ukuxabana phakathi kwabelusi bezifuyo zikaAbrama labelusi bezifuyo zikaLothi\x + 26.20.\x*. Ngalesosikhathi lamaKhanani\x + 12.6.\x* lamaPerizi ayehlala elizweni.
\v 8 UAbrama wasesithi kuLothi: Kakungabi khona-ke ukuxabana phakathi kwami lawe, laphakathi kwabelusi bami labelusi bakho, ngoba singamadoda angabazalwane\x + Seb. 7.26.\x*.
\v 9 Ilizwe lonke kaliphambi kwakho yini\x + 20.15; 34.10.\x*? Yehlukana-ke lami; uba \add usiya\add* ngakwesokhohlo, ngizakuya ngakwesokunene\x + 19.17. Dute. 34.3. Josh. 1.7.\x*; kodwa uba ngakwesokunene, ngizakuya ngakwesokhohlo.
\v 10 ULothi wasephakamisa amehlo akhe, wabona lonke igceke leJordani\x + 19.17. Dute. 34.3. Josh. 1.7.\x* ukuthi lalithelelwe kuhle lonke. IN\sc KOSI\sc* ingakachithi iSodoma leGomora\x + 19.24,25.\x*, \add lali\add*njengensimu yeN\sc KOSI\x + 2.8. Isa. 51.3. Jow. 2.3.\x*\sc*, njengelizwe leGibithe, nxa usiya eZowari\x + 14.2,8; 19.22.\x*.
\v 11 ULothi wasezikhethela lonke igceke leJordani; uLothi-ke waya empumalanga; basebezehlukanisa omunye lomunye.
\v 12 UAbrama wahlala elizweni leKhanani, uLothi wasehlala emizini yemagcekeni, wamisa ithente \add lakhe\add* eduze leSodoma.
\v 13 Kodwa abantu beSodoma babebabi\x + 18.20. Hez. 16.49. 2 Pet. 2.7,8.\x* babeyizoni phambi kweN\sc KOSI\x + 6.11.\x*\sc* kakhulu.
\p
\v 14 IN\sc KOSI\sc* yasisithi kuAbrama emva kokuthi uLothi esehlukaniswe laye: Phakamisa-ke amehlo akho, ukhangele endaweni lapho okhona, ngasenyakatho langaseningizimu langasempumalanga langasentshonalanga\x + 28.14.\x*,
\v 15 ngoba ilizwe lonke olibonayo ngizalinika wena\x + 17.8; 28.13; 35.12. Seb. 7.5.\x*, lakunzalo yakho\x + 12.7; 15.18; 24.7; 26.4. Dute. 34.4. 2 Lan. 20.7.\x* kuze kube nininini.
\v 16 Njalo ngizakwenza inzalo yakho ibe njengothuli lomhlaba\x + 15.5; 22.17; 26.4; 28.14; 32.12. Nani 23.10.\x*, kuze kuthi uba umuntu engabala uthuli lomhlaba, izabalwa lenzalo yakho.
\v 17 Sukuma uhambe udabule ilizwe, ebudeni balo lebubanzini balo, ngoba ngizalinika wena.
\v 18 UAbrama wasesusa amathente wafika wahlala ezihlahleni zamaokhi* zeMamre, eziseHebroni\x + 35.27; 37.14.\x*, wakhela lapho iN\sc KOSI\sc* ilathi.
